<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَابُ زَكَاةِ بَهِيمَةِ الأَنْعَامِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تَجِبُ فِي إِبِلٍ وَبَقَرٍ وَغَنَمٍ، إِذَا كَانَتْ سَائِمَةَ الحَوْلِ أَوْ أَكْثَرِهِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">فَيَجِبُ فِي خَمْسٍ وَعِشْرِينَ مِنَ الإِبِلِ:</span> بِنْتُ مَخَاضٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَفِيمَا دُونَهَا:</span> فِي كُلِّ خَمْسٍ شَاةٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَفِي سِتٍّ وثَلَاثِينَ:</span> بَنِتُ لَبُونٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَفِي سِتٍّ وَأَرْبَعِينَ:</span> حِقَّةٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وَفِي إِحْدَى وَسِتِّينَ:</span> جَذَعَةٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَفِي سِتٍّ وَسَبْعِينَ:</span> بِنْتَا لَبُونٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وَفِي إِحْدَى وَتِسْعِينَ:</span> حِقَّتَانِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">فَإِذَا زَادَتْ عَلَى مِئَةٍ وَعِشْرِينَ وَاحِدَةً:</span> فَثَلَاثُ بَنَاتِ لَبُونٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">ثُمَّ فِي كُلِّ أَرْبَعِينَ:</span> بِنْتُ لَبُونٍ،<span class="c5"> وَفِي كُلِّ خَمْسِينَ:</span> حِقَّةٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>